{"tid":18703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［人口老化］係寶定係賊？","createTime":"2016-12-02T12:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T12:12:24.000Z","uid":51619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3436603ef88afde621d12e7f920a097a98220c47","tid":18703,"uid":51619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T12:12:24.000Z","msg":"細果陣，會覺得長者係好有智慧，會指導你，講下D經驗教下你野咁。<br />\n<br />\n但人越大，個睇法就開始變，覺得佢地食古不化，倚老賣老，無知，只覺得自己果套就一定岩，後生果班就一定錯。特別係d職場老屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為屋企由細到大都無長者一齊住，只係同雙親居住。所以想問下，係咪得我咁偏激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老而不死是為賊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家有一老如有一寶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}